SUMMARY:Winter Walk Long Branch Return Via Etobicoke Creek Trail
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Bike Meetup\n10 km (9.95) winter walk at 4 km per hour
  pace (or faster by consensus) from Long Branch Return Via Etobicoke Creek
  Trail.\n\n1 PM Meet at Long Branch GO station\, 20 Brow Dr\, Etobicoke\, 
 ON M8W 3P6\n\n1 PM to 2 PM Eat at 241 Pizza\, 3815 Lake Shore Blvd W\, Eto
 bicoke\, ON M8W 1R2\, [(416) 241-0241](https://www.google.com/search?q=241
 +pizza+near+longbranch&rlz=1C1RXMK_enCA1182CA1182&ie=UTF-8#)\n\n2 PM to 4:
 30 PM Walk North up Etobicoke Creek Trail to Sherway Dr. Then return south
  to the lake. Finally return to Long branch GO station.\n\nRoute Map with 
 GPX Download:\nhttps://www.komoot.com/tour/2775245111\n\nWear loose fittin
 g winter clothing: coat\, hat\, gloves\, snow pants\, thick socks\, waterp
 roof thermal lined boots with non slip soles. If necessary put warmers in 
 your gloves and boots. Bring water.\n\nChris 647 453 3327
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/torontobikemeetup/events/313321506/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260212T053801Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260212T053801Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
